Class ExecutionStateIMPL

java.lang.Object
implementation.request.ExecutionStateIMPL
All Implemented Interfaces:
fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.requests.interfaces.ExecutionStateI, Serializable
public class ExecutionStateIMPL extends Object implements fr.sorbonne_u.cps.sensor_network.requests.interfaces.ExecutionStateI

Description

The class acts as the implementation of the ExecutionStateI interface. It is used to store the state of the execution of a request on a node.

See the interface ExecutionStateI
